-l-oreal-elvive-dream-lengths-frizz\u0026#34;}\" data-vars-ga-call-to-action=\"$7 at Walmart\" data-vars-ga-media-role=\"1\" data-vars-ga-media-type=\"Embedded Gallery List\" data-vars-ga-outbound-link=\"https://www.walmart.com/ip/297032117?selected=true\" data-vars-ga-product-brand=\"L\u0026#39;Oréal\" data-vars-ga-product-id=\"a6b36ee8-c74b-45c2-8024-fe5368af922d\" data-vars-ga-product-price=\"$7.17\" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id=\"a9226ed9-ec0b-4a6c-a512-49db39f5f5db\" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-brand=\"L\u0026#39;Oréal\" data-vars-ga-gallery-display=\"list\" data-vars-ga-link-treatment=\"sale | (not set)\" data-vars-ga-sku=\"297032117\" data-vars-ga-magento-tracking=\"1\"\u003e\u003cdiv data-theme-key=\"embedded-product-image-container\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/vader-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/1751296860-2621584.png?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=640:* 640w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/vader-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/1751296860-2621584.png?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=980:* 980w\" alt=\"Elvive Dream Lengths Frizz Killer Serum Leave-In\" title=\"Elvive Dream Lengths Frizz Killer Serum Leave-In\" src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/vader-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/1751296860-2621584.png?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=980:*\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cdiv size=\"large\"\u003e\u003ch6\u003eL\u0026#39;Oréal Elvive Dream Lengths Frizz Killer Serum Leave-In\u003c/h6\u003e\u003cp\u003eNow 20% Off\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"lay-off-the-heat\" data-node-id=\"24\"\u003eLay off the heat. \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"26\"\u003eDueñas offered a quick science lesson that might convince you to put down the straightener. “Laying off the heat is never a bad idea,” he says. “Frizz happens when your hair lacks moisture. To compensate, it spreads out, increasing surface area to draw moisture from the air. The more hydrated your hair is, the less frizz you’ll see. So if you use less heat, your hair retains more natural moisture—meaning less frizz.” Simple as that. \u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"get-a-haircut-frequently\" data-node-id=\"28\"\u003eGet a haircut frequently. \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"29\"\u003eDueñas recommends his clients get a haircut “about once every two months,” he says. The benefits of getting more frequent haircuts is twofold, says Dueñas. Split ends are major culprits in causing frizz. The frayed hairs lose moisture quicker and contribute to frizz. Plus, split hairs just looks fuzzy, making it appear as if your already frizzy hair is worse than it even is. In other words, it might be time for you to schedule an appointment.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"wash-your-hair-but-not-too-much\" data-node-id=\"30\"\u003eWash your hair, but not too much.\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"31\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-node-id=\"31.0\"\u003e\u003c/strong\u003eThe consensus among stylists? If you’re prone to frizz, limit washing to once or twice a week. It’s all about balance. “Washing your hair too often strips it of natural moisture, leading to frizz,” says Dueñas. “Too infrequently, and you risk flat strands or product buildup, depending on your natural oils.” As the saying goes: everything in moderation—including moderation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"sleep-on-it\" data-node-id=\"32\"\u003eSleep on it. \u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdiv size=\"medium\" data-embed=\"body-image\" data-lazy-id=\"P0-14\" data-node-id=\"33\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Linens, \" title=\"Linens, \" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"2000\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/elle-sleep-haircare-1506621442.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=320:* 640w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/elle-sleep-haircare-1506621442.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=480:* 980w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/elle-sleep-haircare-1506621442.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=640:* 1120w\" src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/elle-sleep-haircare-1506621442.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=640:*\"/\u003e\u003ca target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-theme-key=\"base-link\" href=\"https://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www.elle.com/beauty/hair/a65253093/how-to-get-rid-frizzy-hair-explained/\u0026amp;description=\u0026amp;media=https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/elle-sleep-haircare-1506621442.jpg?resize=1600:*\"\u003e\u003cimg data-dynamic-svg=\"true\" src=\"https://www.elle.com/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/social/pinterest.e8cf655.svg?primary=%2523ffffff\" loading=\"lazy\" data-testid=\"dynamic-svg-base\" height=\"auto\" width=\"auto\" alt=\"pinterest\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption data-theme-key=\"photo-credit-figcaption\"\u003e\u003cspan data-theme-key=\"photo-credit-creditor\"\u003eCourtsey\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"35\"\u003eThere are ways to fight the frizz while you’re resting, giving true meaning to the phrase “beauty sleep.\u0026#34; Dueñas recommends sleeping in a hair mask covered by a shower cap once a week and says to invest in a silk pillowcase, like \u003ca href=\"https://www.amazon.com/ZIMASILK-Mulberry-Pillowcase-Momme-Queen/dp/B01LW5QIVO?tag=elle_auto-append-20\" target=\"_blank\" data-vars-ga-outbound-link=\"https://www.amazon.com/ZIMASILK-Mulberry-Pillowcase-Momme-Queen/dp/B01LW5QIVO\" data-vars-ga-ux-element=\"Hyperlink\" data-vars-ga-call-to-action=\"ZIMASILK’s silk pillowcase\" data-vars-ga-product-id=\"7cba8ee0-400b-44cc-97dd-930b4c78d683\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-node-id=\"35.1\" data-href=\"https://www.amazo